Works in ALL versions
 
- name: Ensure SSH key is present for rlms user
  hosts: all
  become: yes

  tasks:
    - name: Ensure .ssh directory exists
      file:
        path: /home/rlms/.ssh
        state: directory
        owner: rlms
        group: rlms
        mode: '0700'

    - name: Ensure authorized_keys file exists
      file:
        path: /home/rlms/.ssh/authorized_keys
        state: touch
        owner: rlms
        group: rlms
        mode: '0600'

    - name: Add public key only if not present
      authorized_key:
        user: rlms
        state: present
        key: "ssh-rsa AAAAB3NzaC1yc2EAAAADAQABAAABAQC..."


---------------------------------

- name: Add key (auto handles most cases)
  authorized_key:
    user: rlms
    state: present
    key: "ssh-rsa AAAA..."

This will:
	•	Create .ssh if missing ✅
	•	Create authorized_keys if missing ✅
	•	Add key only if needed ✅

